{"type": "article", "id": 21979, "title": "小鸟灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-05T08:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135012NMFyejHguLlTG269.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">以色列设计师从鸟的翅膀出发设计了这组小鸟灯。它的侧面是细长的等腰梯形，两个斜面掏空，让灯光从两头出来。灯罩是微微倾斜的，恰如小鸟斜立的姿态，简单优美。这款灯的灯罩是橡木制作的，方向可调，里面有一个灯泡。有吊灯、台灯和落地灯多种。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135009UKmL7GZx2ib8AOpe.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24694377\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135010f7zgdjAGlVNwuDQK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.46699267\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135011wSaN8xWbTY23yrQ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18581907\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135011MvK9m5Rwf0rPUDWL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135012LlpVK8XPfqzDyu3T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}